
                                            StatsSA reports that on average, prices increased by 0.3% between September 2017 and October 2017. 
                                         PRETORIA - StatsSA has announced that the headline CPI annual inflation rate in October 2017 was 4.8%. This rate was 0.3 of a percentage point lower than the corresponding annual rate of 5.1% in September 2017. On average, prices increased by 0.3% between September 2017 and October 2017.  More to follow.